dct_title_s: North Western America : showing the territory ceded by Russia to the United States
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings and isolines.; "Drawn by A. Lindenkohl ; Chas G. Krebs, Lith"--Lower margin.; "Second edition, May 1867."; Shows "Russian settlements, Esquimaux settlements."; Scale given in statute and nautical miles.; Depths given in fathoms.; Includes inset: Sitka and its approaches : from Russian and British authorities. Scale 1:200,000, and location map.
